{"tid":1437182,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(代發) 813 燃點香港！衆生覺醒！啟建盂蘭盆顯密念佛煙供大法會","createTime":"2019-08-09T12:53:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T07:15:40.000Z","uid":283572,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"086f457db263c866e7d2bc05122f4daee625a089","tid":1437182,"uid":283572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T12:53:21.000Z","msg":"香港蒙難。三界有責。為了宣揚佛陀正法。拯救香港走出困境，擺脫極權。<br />\n<br />\n將打算借用九龍城亞皆老街盂蘭盆場地舉辦法會。普拖全港幽冥衆生得甘露味。蒙佛音開竅。離苦得樂。為香港積褔種善。<br />\n<br />\n時間:8月13日晚上八點半開始(大勢至菩薩聖誕)<br />\n地點:九龍城亞皆老街足球場<br />\n<br />\n各市民可敬備素菜。糖果等祭品。亦可敬備花香燈塗果等十事濟幽。要煙供的法友請帶備濟幽普施的香粉。不要帶除障粉來。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lifemirror.pixnet.net/blog/post/47978358-%5B%E6%B3%95%E9%96%80%5D-%E7%85%99%E4%BE%9B%E6%B3%95%E5%84%80%E8%BB%8C%E6%99%AE%E5%82%B3%E7%89%88-%28%E4%B8%8A%E5%B8%AB%E8%A8%B1%E5%8F%AF%E7%84%A1%E9%A0%88%E5%8F%A3%E5%82%B3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flifemirror.pixnet.net%2Fblog%2Fpost%2F47978358-%255B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%2596%2580%255D-%25E7%2585%2599%25E4%25BE%259B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%2584%2580%25E8%25BB%258C%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%2582%25B3%25E7%2589%2588-%2528%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E8%25A8%25B1%25E5%258F%25AF%25E7%2584%25A1%25E9%25A0%2588%25E5%258F%25A3%25E5%2582%25B3&d=Zo4i0ptUI%2BsV2bg8TrofrOdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=251b7917\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lifemirror.pixnet.net/blog/post/47978358-%5B%E6%B3%95%E9%96%80%5D-%E7%85%99%E4%BE%9B%E6%B3%95%E5%84%80%E8%BB%8C%E6%99%AE%E5%82%B3%E7%89%88-%28%E4%B8%8A%E5%B8%AB%E8%A8%B1%E5%8F%AF%E7%84%A1%E9%A0%88%E5%8F%A3%E5%82%B3</a><br />\n<br />\n發心出來的别放飛機。否則後果自負<br />\n歡迎入group<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/amitabuddha\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Famitabuddha&d=Zo4i0ptUI%2BsV2bg8TrofrOdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=67991629\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/amitabuddha</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/umZ5G6X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi